[[File:Ringmasters.jpg|right|400px|]]'''Ringmasters''' is the [[Barbershop Harmony Society]]'s 2012 [[BHS International Quartet Champions|International Quartet Champion]] and 2008 [[BHS International Collegiate Quartet Champions | International Collegiate Quartet Champion]]. Hailing from [[SNOBS]], they are also the first affilate quartet to ever win the International Quartet Championship and the second affiliate to ever win the International Collegiate Championship.
== Quartet Members ==
Winning Members: *Tenor: Jacob Stenberg *Lead: Rasmus Krigström *Bari: Emanuel Roll *Bass: Martin Wahlgren
