[[3 Men & A Melody]] is a longtime BHS quartet based in Warsaw City, Missouri. They have advanced to International Semifinalist each year since 2001, and to Finalist in 2004.
== Quartet Members == *Tenor: Robert Mathieu (2011) *Lead: Eric Derks *Bari: Brad Stephens *Bass: Brian Bellof
===Former Members=== *Tenor: Chris Droegemueller (2001-2010)
