== Extended History == *Registered as a quartet in 1995. *After the 2011 contest, 3 Men & A Melody underwent a part change (David Ellis took Robert Mathieu's place as tenor), and the quartet changed its name to Pinnacle, going on to place 23rd in the 2012 International Quartet Contest.
