'''The Con Men''' are the 2012 [[Johnny Appleseed District]] Quartet Champions, the 2013 [[Dealer's Choice Award]] winners, as well as the 2012, 2013, and 2014 College Quartet bronze medalists. They were all born in the same year, so their collegiate competition eligibility came to and end in 2015. All four are members of [[The Alliance Chorus]] of Greater Central Ohio, and are proud to represent the [[Johnny Appleseed District]].
==Quartet Members== *Tenor: David A. Strasser *Lead: Matthew A. Hopper *Bari: Russell T. Watterson *Bass: Brent A. Suver
